change2 Provide a favourite seasons filter

Simple implementation using http query parameter ?series=[ all || number ].
A form dropdown is offered, listing Bobby's favourite series to select from

Test plan
Scenario 1: no query params, show all seasons
Scenario 2: select a favourite from dropdown, show only selected series' episodes
Scenario 3: select All from dropdown, show all seasons
Scenario 4: ?series=999, show No matches